Hello <%= @employee.name %>,

You have been invited to the following meeting:

    Name: <%= @meeting.title %>
    Agenda: <%= @meeting.agenda %>
    Room: <%= @meeting.room.name %> (<%= @meeting.room.room_number %>)
    Location: <%= @meeting.room.location %>
    Start Time: <%= @meeting.start_time.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M%P") %>
    End Time: <%= @meeting.end_time.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M%P") %>
    Attendees:
        <% @meeting.employees.each do |employee| %>
          <%= employee.name %>
        <% end %>

To join this meeting, follow this link and click 'Join': <%= url_for(controller: 'meetings',
                                                                     action: 'show',
                                                                     id: @meeting.id) %>

Sincerely
<%= @meeting.employee.company.name %> Management
